quote: ‘Teaching is the highest form of understanding.’ –Aristotle
description: Assisted in more than *nine courses*, including Advanced Front-End Design, Introduction to Web Development, Object-Oriented Programming, and UX Design. *Evaluated projects and assignments*, while actively engaging in labs to address student questions. This experience sharpened my ability to *analyze diverse coding styles*, deepening my understanding of different approaches to code. This experience also helped me improve my *communication skills and work more effectively with others.*
